Class SubnetsFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx_policy.orgs.projects.vpcs.subnets.SubnetsFactory
  • public class SubnetsFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    SubnetsFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx_policy.orgs.projects.vpcs.subnets package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
